{"tid":2134781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[博奕] 認真諗, 呢期唔好捐血住有著數","createTime":"2020-08-01T03:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T11:27:16.000Z","uid":89641,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d249de121955ba9fbd255eb7ee8ae1f3d3eb26b0","tid":2134781,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"1) 入院果班大部份係藍屍群組、唔怕照去旅行群組, 同幾隻狗<br />\n2) 你捐左未必夠佢地賣上大陸, 只會一直叫你日日捐<br />\n3) 捐血本來就唔係義務, 係出於善心,紅十字會之前發文話3萬警係重要來源, 即係其實我地小市民既血係不重要既一群, 唔洗你咁好心<br />\n4) 而家一窩風去捐,因住惹到武漢肺炎<br />\n5) 過多幾個月又未死先去捐囉"},{"pid":"8233145f12be007e54298ad3576156767b628d4b","tid":2134781,"uid":53122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"三萬 thx就得<br />\n<br />\n洗鬼廢青暴徒d黃血"},{"pid":"698a3b03fb038d6a1a1b52056c46f256d7221822","tid":2134781,"uid":123738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"邊個話唔夠血呀？有三萬隻狗捐噃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c44f3972f6c4fae25e7b1519d050c1422223800","tid":2134781,"uid":197157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"第3點真係最重要<br />\n好心紅十字會有咩事就搵返班黑警捐啦<br />\n關我哋呢啲小市民撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋又唔公開透明，憑咩要人捐<br />\n你係冇賣血咪公開出嚟畀大家還你清白囉<br />\n咩啊，驚啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121b383acd8f203f2a2cf47d7cb6886ea3874148","tid":2134781,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f24548b1713326992c6a998ad94bf642bbfd0d79","tid":2134781,"uid":171313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:42:35.000Z","msg":"藍十字只係多謝黑警<br />\n當班市民嘅血唔係血"},{"pid":"d458dfe8ea7675fecc86cd744fa3eff0d7e30fd1","tid":2134781,"uid":209241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"除左第5點之外, 其他都好同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fb2f928e4c28e551836861b21c118cc4fbe8c0","tid":2134781,"uid":140104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"唔捐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8485d62f67509d6803dac1c3e16f01965c0e171","tid":2134781,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88171a0662f5f7cdba820e5151bc272f0f470c0f","tid":2134781,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"99c5f6ffc0d20f117c265b8a629a5f475d239b72","tid":2134781,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"邊期都唔會捐"},{"pid":"d08fd415d0a441a3afdc5e202be740caec013475","tid":2134781,"uid":49876,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nuj5eb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNuj5eb7.jpg&h=294c867b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩年告急完 多人去捐血啦<br />\n點知仲要比紅十字會串<br />\n我都係聽返佢指示 就算告急都唔好去捐<br />\n廢事全港都一窩蜂去捐啦"},{"pid":"caf99db06f4c7b25ff117792338e569af98d03e5","tid":2134781,"uid":121940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"我成世都唔會捐<br />\n除左中學果次捐完會加番操行分<br />\n我同自己講身體髮膚受之父母 就算捐都淨係捐比父母<br />\n老豆老母比個身體我 要捐器官都係比父母"},{"pid":"6521ed2cb6c56e945ee035e3c8979284d3f947ca","tid":2134781,"uid":128991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"驚俾人順便攞走我嘅DNA，不了"},{"pid":"61f2d11c4bc69886cb5721301612569e525be3d1","tid":2134781,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"其實